text: Meller-Zakomelsky or Möller-Sakomelski/Sakomelsky is a Russian surname of German and noble origins. It may refer to: *Alexander Meller-Zakomelsky (1844–1928) — Imperial Russian Governor of Livonia and General *Ivan Möller- Sakomelsky (1725–1790) — General of the Russian Empire ==See also== *Meller * Category:Russian noble families Category:Compound surnames Category:Russian- language surnames Category:Surnames of German origin
title: Meller-Zakomelsky
